    "text": "I am leaving Avast and looking for new things to do.\nMy dream job would be to dive into data and thus help develop some useful service or mobile app.\n\nI can:\n🗄️ write SQL\n📈 use Google Analytics, Firebase Analytics, GDocs & Excel, GitHub, Stack Overflow, PowerBI, Kibana; I learned a bit of Python and Pandas in Jupyter\n📲 create user campaigns, segmentation, A/B testing\n📊 design research and report statistical results\n👩‍💻 learn new technologies – I'm not afraid of tech stuff\n🔊 organise conferences and events; host them and speak in public\n🇬🇧 translate and proofread Czech and English texts\n\nGet in touch 😉 \n#data #analytics #sql",
